title: The Killing of Freddie Gray, Episode 8 – Illusion of Transparency
description:
April 24, 2017 / Baltimore police released video from 16 cameras and audio dispatch at trial supposedly capturing the van’s route to the public.  Why does so much of this evidence not add up?
